body.
Chloe got sleepy while the movie was on, so she decided to lie down on
Carter and use him as a makeshift bed. Currently, she is fast asleep like a
little angel with one small arm curled around his neck. Her other hand is
wrapped around his side so that she’s basically hugging him while she
sleeps.
