I’m not sure funny is the word, but it’s certainly remarkable how
different things are from how they were before Carter. When I was nobody,
when I reported Jake’s behavior, not a single person sprang to my defense.
Not even my own parents. Now, Jake is a little bit unpleasant to me and I
have cheerleaders and parents running to my rescue, all because now that
