even when he’s no longer around to make it count.
Or maybe not. Who knows?
At least I’ve survived the worst of senior year. From now until
graduation, aside from jealous jerks trying to shake my trust in Carter for no
reason, I have a hunch things will be calm. By the time I get used to it, it
will be time for college to separate us, and I’ll begin a whole new adventure
