My heart feels emptier just thinking about it. There’s no reason to let
concerns about the future dull the present, though. Shoving them aside, I
enjoy the feeling of Carter’s strong arms locking around my waist, his
kisses peppering my mouth before he claims it in a deep, possessive kiss.
